--     V3.1 2012-06-26 Add unisFlhPartBootable and unisFlhPartPathForGlobalOpt
--                     by lisong.
--     V3.2 2013-05-23 Add unisFlhHCSize, unisFlhPartHCSpace,
--                     unisFlhPartHCSpaceFree and unisFlhFileHCSize to replace
--                     unisFlhSize, unisFlhPartSpace, unisFlhPartSpaceFree
--                     and unisFlhFileSize by lisong.
--     V3.3 2014-08-11 Added mkdir(6), rmdir(7) to unisFlhOperType, added unisFlhFileType
--                     to unisFlhFileEntry, modified description of
--                     unisFlhFileName, unisFlhOperProtocol, unisFlhOperSourceFile
